long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Modify YouTube thumbnails to include James the Duck
Enhance your browsing experience with James the Duck. Is your browser experience boring? Are you having trouble finding engaging click-baity videos? Fear no more. This extension adds our mascot James the Duck to every thumbnail.

Compatible with all browsers
